# youchop.app — server env (set these in the Vercel project, not committed)

# youtube-transcript.io API token, from Profile → API.
# Paste ONLY the token value — the code prepends "Basic " itself, so do not include
# the word "Basic".
# Plus plan ($9.99/mo) is required for the channel search endpoint (/api/channels);
# the transcripts endpoint works on any paid tier. https://www.youtube-transcript.io/pricing
#
# Set it live with:  vercel env add YT_TRANSCRIPT_TOKEN production   (then redeploy)
YT_TRANSCRIPT_TOKEN=
